<h4 id="为普通用户添加root权限">为普通用户添加root权限</h4>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># 在"root ALL=(ALL) ALL"添加一行</span>
username <span class="nv">ALL</span><span class="o">=(</span>All<span class="o">)</span>  ALL
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="1-group">1. group</h4>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># add group</span>
groupadd docker
<span class="c"># user modify</span>
usermod <span class="nt">-aG</span> docker <span class="nv">$USER</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="2-user">2. User</h4>
<p>Add a new user as sudoer using command line</p>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># this change will take effect the next time the user logs in</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>adduser &lt;username&gt; <span class="nb">sudo</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
